    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever wondered how much damage your car can take?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will it survive a collision with a tree? How about hitting a concrete wall? Have you ever considered of the damages your vehicle might get after you slightly touch the side of another car while going 80 km/h?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Well, now you can recreate the aftermath of such an accident: cracks, rust, dents, scratches...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All this damage, plus a set of new &quot;Sponsored&quot; stickers, will allow you to start writing a unique history of your drift car, without limiting your imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This will be the history of your car, and you're going to be its author.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 200 of new stickers from HIT THE WALL DLC is all you need for it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The DLC also includes skins for:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Phoenix NX</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wütend</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Burner JDM</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Samurai II</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carrot II</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have fun!</p>",
